quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  89,1,"Mi wooɗndirii Fajira."
  89,2,"Mi wooɗndirii balɗe sappa."
  89,3,"Mi wooɗndirii kala ko ɗimmita e ko teelɗi."
  89,4,"Mi wooɗndarii jehma si mbo arii e niɓɓidde."
  89,5,"Mbele ina e ndee wooɗndoore jaɓnoore joom hakkille."
  89,6,"Mbele a yi'aani na joom ma waɗi Aad en."
  89,7,"Irama joom doosɗe."
  89,8,"Mbo hono mum tagaaka e lesdi."
  89,9,"E Samuud ɓeen se'ekɓe kaaƴe to caatngol."
  89,10,"E Fir'awna joom peŋɗe."
  89,11,"Ɓeen bewnooɓe to lesdi."
  89,12,"Ɓe kebbini e hendi bonan'nde."
  89,13,"Joom ma yuppi e maɓɓe lepte caɗtuɗe."
  89,14,"Koom ma na tommbiiɓe."
  89,15,"Tawi ko neɓɗɗaŋke si joom makko jarabiimo mbo o teddani mbo o neemini mbo o wiat joom am teddinii kam."
  89,16,"Si tawii noon o jaribiimo mbo o faaɗni arsuko makko o wi'a joom am hoynii kam."
  89,17,"Ala wona noon, ko woni ko on teddintaana baaya."
  89,18,"On ndeerɗiŋtaa e ñammiingol miskiino."
  89,19,"Hoɗon ñaama ndonu ñaamgol caɗtungol."
  89,20,"Hoɗon njiɗi jawdi jiɗgol caɗtungol."
  89,21,"Ala ɗuum haanaani, si lesdi ndii dimmbaama dimmbugol."
  89,22,"Joom ma ardi e maleykaaji hiɗi mbaɗi saffeeji."
  89,23,"jahanama addee ñande heen neɗɗo siftoro kono hol ko ciftorgol nafata."
  89,24,"O wi'a haaniino mi ardinii golle lobbe wonan'de nguurndam am."
  89,25,"E oon ñalawma hay gooto leɓtatah hono lepte mum."
  89,26,"Hay go'oto tonngetaake hono tonngi heeferɓe."
  89,27,"Ehey ma fittaandu huɓandiindu."
  89,28,"Rutto e joom ma haɗa woni belaaɗo mbo Kaŋko ne hombo wela ma."
  89,29,"Naat e maccuɓe am."
  89,30,"Naat e aljanna am."
